headline: Jacobs Announced as Program Manager and Owners Engineer for Xcel Energy
summary: Jacobs (NYSE: J) was selected as Program Manager and Owners Engineer to support Xcel Energy in providing customers with safe and reliable energy services at a competitive price, while meeting the specifications needed for a low-carbon future.
